{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01692hHm98ahj1uZj5UvMfxt","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→# Implementation History — 101-lord-of-the-rngs\n     2→\n     3→Iteration log for the autonomous spec loop. Each entry records what was\n     4→attempted and whether it succeeded. The agent reads this file at the start\n     5→of every iteration to understand prior context.\n     6→\n     7→---\n     8→\n     9→## Iteration 1 — Scaffold lordofrngs program\n    10→\n    11→**Item**: Phase A, item 1 — Scaffold `solana/programs/lordofrngs/`\n    12→\n    13→**What was done**:\n    14→- Created `programs/lordofrngs/` directory with full structure:\n    15→  - `Cargo.toml` — mirrors coinflip dependencies (anchor-lang, rng-shared, platform CPI, orao-solana-vrf), same feature flags including mock-vrf default\n    16→  - `Xargo.toml` — standard BPF target config\n    17→  - `src/lib.rs` — `declare_id!(\"B9Lufh9GvuucDxDRZBr3qPNe4cJaS5MQBQKZxgUT5qYa\")`, program module with `initialize_config` instruction stub\n    18→  - `src/state.rs` — `LordConfig` (PDA `[b\"lord_config\"]`, authority/treasury/paused/round_counters/bump), `PlayerEntry` (player pubkey + u32 entries), `JackpotRound` (PDA `[b\"jackpot_round\", tier, round_number]`, full round state with Vec<PlayerEntry> max 20), `RoundSettled` event\n    19→  - `src/error.rs` — `LordError` enum with 13 error codes (6100–6112)\n    20→  - `src/instructions/mod.rs` + `src/instructions/initialize_config.rs` — config init handler\n    21→- Registered in `solana/Cargo.toml` workspace members\n    22→- Registered in `solana/Anchor.toml` programs (localnet + devnet)\n    23→- Program ID: `B9Lufh9GvuucDxDRZBr3qPNe4cJaS5MQBQKZxgUT5qYa` (Anchor-generated keypair)\n    24→\n    25→**Verification**: `anchor build -p lordofrngs` — **passed** (warnings only, same as coinflip). Coinflip still builds.\n    26→\n    27→**Status**: Done\n    28→\n    29→## Iteration 1 — 2026-02-26T22:05:53Z — OK\n    30→- *